title: Coronavirus: Trump administation says 13,500 Americans stranded overseas have asked for help
description: A task force assembled by the US is working on getting flights out to those seeking assistance so they can get home
content:
The State Department is preparing to evacuate thousands of Americans stranded overseas, with 16 flights scheduled in the next five days and more to follow, officials said Monday.
